## New Features Across All Pages

### Sidebar (2026 Edition)
- **🔍 Search the Loom** — button with `/ ` keyboard shortcut hint
- **Navigate / Discover** section labels organizing links
- **🏪 Marketplace** & **🎭 Events** nav links
- **⏰ Live Guild Clock** — real-time `HH:MM:SS` clock at sidebar bottom

### Global Search Overlay
- Press `/` anywhere to open full-screen search
- Fuzzy match against threads, pages, and artisan names
- Press `Esc` to close, `Enter` to navigate

### Particle Canvas Background
- 80 animated floating gold/purple/crimson particles
- Smooth frame-by-frame animation via `requestAnimationFrame`
- Fixed behind all content, very subtle for atmosphere

### Animated Stat Counters
- Homepage guild stats now count up with easing from 0
- Triggered by Intersection Observer when scrolled into view

### Trending Tags Cloud
- Homepage: `#GothicSpring2026`, `#BlackFlame`, etc.
- Hot tags styled in crimson, regular tags in gold
- Click animation (scale pop)

### Event Banner on Homepage
- Prominent card linking to the active monthly challenge
- "March 2026: Gothic Spring Awakening" with entry count

### Scroll-to-Top Button
- Appears after scrolling 400px
- Smooth scroll + gold glow on hover

### Hero CTA Buttons
- Homepage hero now has "Join the Guild" + "Browse Threads" buttons

